rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Smismi sailing along and happen to see
shadow of sunken ship in Cloud Sea!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0002
rows.name:
One look was all it take to flip switch
of Smismi to adventure mode! Many
visions of treasure and derring-do!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Too much treasure to bring back all
at once! Probably!

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Ah, but Smismi so busy at helm of
Goldmund, not spare moment to
go out exploring.

rows.label: tlk42360111_05_msg0005
rows.name:
Was hoping friends haul treasure out in
place of Smismi. Maybe split earnings
down middle!
